Description:


Remake of the 1994 shooter created by Apogee Software (later became known as 3D Realms). Remake created by the studio Interceptor Entertainment on Unreal Engine
3 and is dedicated to the bloodthirsty showdowns with the fascists. The game will have 5 playable characters with their own abilities, 20 levels and multiplayer mode. The project is created exclusively for the PC.


